    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a definitive collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist. Powered by a naturally aspirated 3.8L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), the engine provides immediate throttle response and linear power delivery through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), featuring recalibrated damping for superior lateral stability. Mechanically, this example is beyond reproach: the valvetrain is whisper-quiet, the cooling system has been pressure-tested, and the undercarriage remains factory-dry with no evidence of seepage. Finished in a show-quality coat with an immaculate cabin, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of analog feedback and modern reliability.",
